categories: Category:Grand Moffs of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Weblin was a Regional Governor serving the Galactic Republic and later the Galactic Empire as a Moff.
When Emperor Palpatine declared his Galactic Empire in 19 BBY, Weblin became Grand Moff of Sector 6 and assumed the role of commander of the 6th Sector Army, better known as Black Sword Command.
A fleet tender of the Imperial Navy, the Moff Weblin, was later named after him.
